Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is delighted to offer 54-58 Lipton Drive, Thomastown for sale. 

This outstanding and strategically located industrial facility sits on the edge of the Metropolitan Ring Road within an established industrial pocket offering direct access to Keon Parade, High Street & Mahoneys Road.

The 3,010sqm* site comprises a large, clear span warehouse of 1,890sqm*, and office/amenities of 240sqm* with generous frontage to Lipton Drive of 55m*. 

The building itself allows access via two separate cross overs and multiple roller doors and encompasses a regular shaped warehouse with cool room, partitioned ground floor offices and ample amenity for staff.

Further highlights include;
- Total building area: 2,140sqm*
- Clear span warehouse: 1,890sqm*
- Ground floor office/amenity: 250sqm* 
- Total land area: 3,010sqm*
- Dual roller door access
- Partitioned ground floor offices
- Potential signage fronting Metropolitan Ring Road
- On-site secured parking for 20 cars
- Cool room
- Immediate access to Metropolitan Ring Road, Keon Parade, Dalton Road, High Street & Mahoneys Road

For an Information Memorandum or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE.

*approx.

The strategically located property will appeal to owner occupiers, investors and developers looking to add further value to the property. 43-47 Northgate Drive is situated within close proximity to major arterials including the Metropolitan Ring Road, Hume Freeway, Settlement Road and Dalton Road allowing unprecedented access to the site.

Key property features include:

+ Gross Lettable Area: 2,723sqm*
+ Total site area: 9,000sqm*
+ Two (2) separate titles
+ Current net passing rent $316,520 pa
+ Opportunity for building expansion or further development (STCA)
 
For further information regarding this opportunity or to arrange an inspection of the site, kindly contact CBRE.

Offered for sale by Expressions of Interest, closing Thursday, 23rd May 2019 at 3.00pm

CBRE is delighted to present Unit 15 at Dalton Link Business Park, Thomastown, for lease.

This exciting new development is located right next to Bunnings along Dalton Road enjoying fantastic access to the Metropolitan Ring Road. Surrounding this development are many bulky-goods retail outlets, service stations, fast food and café amenities.  

Key features include:
+   Total building area: 176sqm*
+   Modern office of 41sqm* including kitchenette 
+   Ground floor area is 134sqm*
+   Three (3) phase power 
+   1 x Container height roller shutter door 
+   Full amenities including 2 x kitchenettes, 2 bathrooms and separate shower 
+   2 exclusive car spaces

Please contact the exclusive marketing agents for inspection and further information.

*approximate

CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer 333 Settlement Road, Thomastown For Sale via Expressions of Interest closing Thursday, 18th March 2021 at 3pm AEDT. 

This strategic acquisition opportunity benefits from excellent surrounding arterial infrastructure including direct access to M80 Metropolitan Ring Road (310m*) as well as being located within immediate proximity to an abundance of retail amenity and public transport connectivity.

Given the diminishing supply of industrial land in Melbourne’s northern precinct, this purchase opportunity is extremely rare and will appeal to owner occupiers and developers looking to capitalise on Thomastown's highly desirable industrial location.

Property details: 
+ Land holding: 18,182sqm*
+ Building area: 5,000sqm*
+ Industrial 1 Zone (IN1Z)

Location Details:
+ M80 Metropolitan Ring Road - 310m*
+ Mahoneys Road - 750m*
+ Hume Highway - 3.4km*
+ Melbourne CBD - 13.9km*

Please contact the exclusive selling agents, CBRE, for further information on 333 Settlement Road, Thomastown.

EXPRESSIONS OF INTEREST CLOSING THURSDAY 18TH MARCH, 2021 AT 3PM (AEDT).

Charter Keck Cramer - Transaction Advisor.

*approx.

Key property attributes include:
